[I] The ROCm Validation Suite

[T] The ROCm Validation Suite (RVS) is a system validation and diagnostics tool
[T] for monitoring, stress testing, detecting and troubleshooting issues that
[T] affects the functionality and performance of AMD GPU(s) operating in a
[T] high-performance/AI/ML computing environment. RVS is enabled using the ROCm
[T] software stack on a compatible software and hardware platform.

[U] https://github.com/ROCm/ROCmValidationSuite

